1. Create hokuyo.urdf.xacro at '/opt/ros/kinetic/share/turtlebot_description/urdf/sensors' as presented
2. Create kobuki_hexagons_hokuyo.urdf.xacro at '/opt/ros/kinetic/share/turtlebot_description/robots' as presented
3. (sudo) Edit '/opt/ros/kinetic/share/turtlebot_description/urdf/turtlebot_gazebo.urdf.xacro' as presented
4. (sudo) Edit '/opt/ros/kinetic/share/turtlebot_description/urdf/turtlebot_common_library.urdf.xacro' as presented
5. (sudo) Copy file '/opt/ros/kinetic/share/gazebo_plugins/test/multi_robot_scenario/meshes/laser/hokuyo.dae'
    to '/opt/ros/kinetic/share/turtlebot_description/meshes/sensors'
6. Add the following line at the end of your ~/.bashrc: export TURTLEBOT_3D_SENSOR="hokuyo"
